>\r\nThis Chanel product is a oh-my-god-so-good baked peach blush with a marbleesque finish. With gold shot spread evenly it doubles up as a great highlighter and gives an impressive glow to your face.', 'Quote Format', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '277-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-21 10:53:07', '2016-03-21 10:53:07', '', 277, 'http://192.168.9.75/march/cosmetro/wordpress/2016/03/21/277-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
